  <brief_title>Paris Visual Learning Test: a New French Task for Assess Visual Learning and Memory to Multiple Sclerosis Patients</brief_title>
  <acronym>valid-PVLT</acronym>
  <official_title>Paris Visual Learning Test (PVLT): a New French Task for Assess Visual Learning and Memory to Multiple Sclerosis Patients</official_title>
